Class StaffEdit

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.StaffEdit

  • public class StaffEdit
extends java.lang.Object
    This class allows staff/librarians to view and edit their details when they register to the system. Also, they can edit some information and update it back to the database with their latest information.

    leezhinghang
